- problem_statement.odt
TrackHub registry development: problem description, assumption and risk factors.

- draft-trackhub-01.json
JSON schema to represent the properties of a TrackHub - draft version 01.
This is an attempt to model in JSON the display and configuration properties of the UCSC trackhub specification. Hierarchical (i.e. super, composite, aggregate) tracks are included. 

- draft-trackhub-02.json
JSON schema to represent the properties of a UCSC TrackHub - draft version 02.
Attempt to separate the data/metadata definition from the presentation layer. This has been expressed as a desirable goal by David Bujold and his team of the IHEC (International Human Epigenomics Consortium).

-search.txt
Includes notes and observations specific to searching track hubs.